at the bottom of some
of our deeper mine shafts.

01:27:56.992 --> 01:28:01.828
The radioactivity would never penetrate
a mine some thousands of feet deep.

01:28:01.898 --> 01:28:06.165
And in a matter of weeks, sufficient
improvements in dwelling space...

01:28:06.237 --> 01:28:08.171
could easily be provided.

01:28:08.239 --> 01:28:11.003
How long would you have
to stay down there?

01:28:11.075 --> 01:28:14.944
Well, that's, you know...

01:28:15.013 --> 01:28:17.675
Cobalt thorium G.

01:28:27.928 --> 01:28:31.762
Radioactive half-life of...

01:28:33.834 --> 01:28:38.568
I would think that possibly
one hundred years.

01:28:40.909 --> 01:28:44.903
You mean, people could actually
stay down there for 100 years?

01:28:44.981 --> 01:28:47.211
<i>It would not be difficult,
Mein Fuhrer.</i>

01:28:47.283 --> 01:28:49.514
Nuclear reactors could...

01:28:49.586 --> 01:28:51.952
I'm sorry, Mr. President.

01:28:52.022 --> 01:28:55.822
Nuclear reactors could provide
power almost indefinitely.

01:28:55.892 --> 01:28:58.726
Greenhouses could maintain
plant life.

01:28:58.796 --> 01:29:02.391
Animals could be bred
and slaughtered.

01:29:02.467 --> 01:29:06.905
A quick survey would have to be made of
the available mine sites in the country.

01:29:06.972 --> 01:29:10.773
But I would guess
that a dwelling space...

01:29:10.844 --> 01:29:14.507
for several hundred thousand of
our people could easily be provided.

01:29:14.581 --> 01:29:17.709
Well, I would hate
to have to decide...

01:29:17.785 --> 01:29:20.686
who stays up and who goes down.

01:29:20.755 --> 01:29:24.657
Well, that would not be
necessary, Mr. President.

01:29:24.725 --> 01:29:27.593
It could easily be accomplished
with a computer.

01:29:27.662 --> 01:29:29.960
And the computer could
be set and programmed...

01:29:30.032 --> 01:29:33.093
to accept factors
from youth, health...

01:29:33.169 --> 01:29:36.332
sexual fertility, intelligence...

01:29:36.406 --> 01:29:38.897
and a cross-section
of necessary skills.

01:29:38.975 --> 01:29:41.240
Of course, it would be
absolutely vital...

01:29:41.311 --> 01:29:45.270
that our top government
and military men be included...

01:29:45.349 --> 01:29:50.185
to foster and impart the required
principles of leadership and tradition.

01:29:56.228 --> 01:29:59.163
Naturally, they would breed
prodigiously.

01:29:59.231 --> 01:30:02.030
There would be much time
and little to do.

01:30:03.637 --> 01:30:08.575
But with the proper breeding techniques
and a ratio of, say...

01:30:08.643 --> 01:30:11.407
ten females to each male...

01:30:11.479 --> 01:30:16.110
they could then work their way back
to the present gross national product...

01:30:16.185 --> 01:30:17.948
within 20 years.

01:30:19.154 --> 01:30:21.884
But look, Doctor.
Wouldn't this nucleus of survivors...

01:30:21.957 --> 01:30:27.055
be so grief-stricken
and anguished that they...

01:30:27.130 --> 01:30:30.623
well, envy the dead
and not want to go on living?

01:30:30.701 --> 01:30:33.534
No, sir. Excuse me.

01:30:42.814 --> 01:30:46.751
When they go down into the mine,
everyone would still be alive.

01:30:46.819 --> 01:30:48.912
There would be
no shocking memories...

01:30:48.988 --> 01:30:53.653
and the prevailing emotion will be one
of nostalgia for those left behind...

01:30:53.727 --> 01:30:56.594
combined with a spirt of...

01:30:56.663 --> 01:30:59.098
bold curiosity for
the adventure ahead!

01:31:16.620 --> 01:31:18.554
Doctor...

01:31:20.758 --> 01:31:26.196
you mentioned the ratio
of ten women to each man.

01:31:26.264 --> 01:31:29.393
Now, wouldn't that
necessitate the abandonment...

01:31:29.468 --> 01:31:33.268
of the so-called
monogamous sexual relationship?

01:31:33.338 --> 01:31:36.968
I mean, as far as men were concerned?

01:31:37.043 --> 01:31:38.408
Regrettably, yes.

01:31:38.478 --> 01:31:43.849
But it is a sacrifice required
for the future of the human race.

01:31:43.918 --> 01:31:48.913
I hasten to add that since each man
will be required to do prodigious...

01:31:50.692 --> 01:31:52.626
service along these lines...

01:31:52.694 --> 01:31:56.495
the women will have to be selected
for their sexual characteristics...

01:31:56.566 --> 01:32:00.332
which will have to be of
a highly stimulating nature.

01:32:00.403 --> 01:32:04.238
I must confess, you have an
astonishingly good idea there, Doctor.

01:32:05.409 --> 01:32:06.842
Thank you, sir.

01:32:06.910 --> 01:32:09.880
We ought to look at this
from the military point of view.

01:32:09.948 --> 01:32:13.884
I mean,
supposing the Ruskies...

01:32:13.952 --> 01:32:16.887
stashed away some big bombs,
see, and we didn't?

01:32:16.955 --> 01:32:19.857
When they come out in 100 years,
they could take over!

01:32:19.925 --> 01:32:21.688
I agree, Mr. President.

01:32:21.760 --> 01:32:25.356
They might try a sneak attack so they
could take over our mine shaft space.

01:32:25.432 --> 01:32:30.062
It'd be extremely naive of us to
imagine that these new developments...

01:32:30.136 --> 01:32:33.072
are gonna cause any change
in Soviet expansionist policy!

01:32:33.140 --> 01:32:35.973
I mean, we must be
increasingly on the alert...

01:32:36.043 --> 01:32:38.569
to prevent them from taking over
other mine shaft space...

01:32:38.647 --> 01:32:40.581
in order to breed more
prodigiously than we do...

01:32:40.649 --> 01:32:43.777
thus knocking us out through
superior numbers when we emerge!

01:32:43.852 --> 01:32:47.949
Mr. President, we must not allow
a mine-shaft gap!

01:32:48.024 --> 01:32:50.117
Sir!

01:32:50.193 --> 01:32:52.457
I have a plan...

01:32:53.998 --> 01:32:56.330
<i>Mein Fuhrer...</i>

01:32:56.400 --> 01:32:58.994
I can walk!

